 a cape"},{"s":16.6,"e":19.5,"text":"Till they fell off my back"},{"s":20.52,"e":23,"text":"Looked in the glass and said"},{"s":23,"e":24.96,"text":"You can build from a crack"},{"s":24.96,"e":28.2,"text":"Told myself, “Rise up now”"},{"s":28.2,"e":31.18,"text":"And my bones said, “Try it”"},{"s":31.18,"e":33.7,"text":"If I can name it, I can chase it"},{"s":33.7,"e":36.46,"text":"If I can pray it, I can buy it"},{"s":36.46,"e":39.42,"text":"But I know my hands are shaky"},{"s":39.42,"e":42.22,"text":"I know my heart can lie"},{"s":42.22,"e":45.08,"text":"So I keep one eye on heaven"},{"s":45.08,"e":48.04,"text":"And one eye on the sky"},{"s":48.04,"e":49.44,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":49.44,"e":53.52,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":53.52,"e":57.92,"text":"With belief in my veins"},{"s":57.92,"e":59.28,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":59.74,"e":61.98,"text":"Jesus, hold my bets"},{"s":61.98,"e":64.96,"text":"When my power runs thin"},{"s":64.96,"e":67.74,"text":"I can rise on my own"},{"s":67.74,"e":71.2,"text":"But I’d rather rise with Him"},{"s":72.32,"e":74.7,"text":"Now I’m swinging from the curb"},{"s":74.7,"e":77.5,"text":"Like a kid in a sheet"},{"s":77.5,"e":81.06,"text":"Calling out my own name"},{"s":81.06,"e":83.2,"text":"In the dust of the street"},{"s":83.2,"e":86.2,"text":"And if I save one stranger"},{"s":86.2,"e":88.94,"text":"Then I save some part of me"},{"s":88.94,"e":91.84,"text":"Still I need that mercy"},{"s":91.84,"e":94.64,"text":"Like the river needs the sea"},{"s":94.64,"e":97.68,"text":"I know I’m only human"},{"s":97.68,"e":100.3,"text":"Trying on a flame"},{"s":100.3,"e":103.12,"text":"I can wear the mask, the cape"},{"s":103.12,"e":106.16,"text":"Still I whisper Your name"},{"s":106.16,"e":107.48,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":107.48,"e":111.54,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":111.54,"e":116.04,"text":"With belief in my veins"},{"s":116.04,"e":117.38,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":117.84,"e":120.08,"text":"Jesus, hold my bets"},{"s":120.08,"e":122.98,"text":"When my power runs thin"},{"s":122.98,"e":125.8,"text":"I can rise on my own"},{"s":125.8,"e":128.7,"text":"But I’d rather rise with Him"},{"s":128.7,"e":133.02,"text":"So thank you, St. John’s"},{"s":133.02,"e":135.74,"text":"For the bowls and the grace"},{"s":135.74,"e":138.8,"text":"For the men with tired eyes"},{"s":138.8,"e":141.42,"text":"And the names I can’t replace"},{"s":141.42,"e":143.98,"text":"If I wasn’t down so low"},{"s":143.98,"e":146.96,"text":"I might never understand"},{"s":146.96,"e":149.9,"text":"How a borrowed cup of soup"},{"s":149.9,"e":152.92,"text":"Can put strength in a man"},{"s":152.92,"e":154.22,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":154.22,"e":158.08,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":158.08,"e":162.7,"text":"With belief in my veins"},{"s":162.7,"e":164.12,"text":"I can be more"},{"s":164.6,"e":166.88,"text":"Jesus, hold my bets"},{"s":166.88,"e":169.74,"text":"When my power runs thin"},{"s":169.74,"e":172.6,"text":"I can rise on my own"},{"s":172.6,"e":175.68,"text":"But I’d rather rise with Him"},{"s":177.24,"e":179.92,"text":"Thank you, St. John’s"},{"s":179.92,"e":182.58,"text":"For the way you showed me"},{"s":182.58,"e":185.7,"text":"A crown can start as nothing"},{"s":185.7,"e":190.4,"text":"And still be holy"}],"duration":202.12,"source":"whisper-aligned","generatedAt":"2026-05-25T06:38:40.279Z","stats":{"whisperWords":339,"polishedWords":334,"matched":330,"matchRate":0.988}}